  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Dabie Mountain Area Community Development Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will assist eight villages that suffered from a destructive snowstorm in Huoshan, Yuexi and Taihu counties. During the project, 400 families will receive high-quality livestock, such as pigs and cattle. Training that covers topics from the 12 Cornerstones and the Values-Based Holistic Community Development model to natural disaster resistance and biogas usage and maintenance will also be provided. This project will give special focus to improving community education levels, health status and strengthening law consciousness. Parents and teachers will be trained on participatory educational concepts and methods that relate to daily life. Knowledge on basic health care will be shared to all community members. Another 590 families will benefit from Passing on the Gift after forming the self-help groups and receiving VBHCD model training from the fist generation groups.</narrative>
  </description>
